dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by shading.
East oriented toward left of sheet.
Decorative cartouche with descriptive text, compass rose, castles, tents, topography.
Depicts battle of Velez de Gomera, showing siege of Pignon by Spanish, Italian, and German troops, with Spanish, Portuguese, and Maltese ships and galleys.
dct_spatial_sm: Peñón de Vélez de la Gomera (Spain)
